OL,6,FWorld War Two killed more people,
OL,7,Fdisrupted more lives, and probably had
OL,8,Fmore far reaching effects than any
OL,9,Fother war in history.
OL,11,FEight decades on, some of the last
OL,12,Fliving veterans have come together to
OL,13,Freflect on and remember their time in
OL,14,Fthe forces.
OL,16,FNine veterans from the Swansea area,
OL,17,Fwith a combined age of more than 900
OL,18,Fyears, attended an event at Mansion
OL,19,FHouse as part of the city's Armed
OL,20,FForces Celebrations.
