OL,6,F"And were you?" I asked him.
OL,8,F"No, not really", he replied with a
OL,9,Fsmirk on his face.
OL,11,FDavid was accepted as a Sea Cadet
OL,12,FOfficer and joined the crew of the
OL,13,FQuebec City on the Atlantic Convoys.
OL,15,FIn 1942, sailing out of Cape Town in
OL,16,Fthe South Atlantic, his vessel was hit
OL,17,Fand sunk by a German U-boat.
OL,19,FThe crew spent 14 days at sea in a
OL,20,Flifeboat with virtually no water until
OL,21,Fthey hit land in Liberia.
