OL,6,FAfter weeks in a jungle village, they
OL,7,Fwere eventually rescued by a British
OL,8,FRoyal Navy crew.
OL,10,FBut there was a silver lining.
OL,12,F"When I came home they put me in
OL,13,FMorriston Military hospital because
OL,14,FI'd damaged my leg. When I was fit to
OL,15,Fwalk, I was interviewed by a senior
OL,16,Fofficer. I liked this lady and I
OL,17,Fdidn't know her name.
