OL,6,F"After I left the base, I wrote to the
OL,7,FCommander of the base and asked him if
OL,8,Fhe could tell me the name of the
OL,9,Fofficer who interviewed me", he said.
OL,11,F"Everyone told me, 'He won't give you
OL,12,Fa name' but he did."
OL,14,FBy the time the Commander answered,
OL,15,FCaptain David was on his way back to
OL,16,Fnorth Africa.
