OL,6,F"I just had a little note from this
OL,7,Flady and I kept writing to her and I
OL,8,Fwas another two and a quarter years in
OL,9,Fthe Mediterranean fleet of seven
OL,10,Finvasions and I just kept writing to
OL,11,Fher.
OL,13,F"Eventually, I came back to the UK,
OL,14,Fback to Swansea and I met this lady.
OL,15,FWe got married within 12 months and we
OL,16,Fwere married for 75 years."
OL,18,FBut not everyone served in the army.
OL,19,FKath Morris was a codebreaker at
OL,20,FBritain's best-kept secret, Bletchley
OL,21,FPark.
