OL,6,FIt was a war that changed the world.
OL,7,FBut the men and women who served for
OL,8,Ftheir country are now part of a
OL,9,Fdisappearing generation.
OL,11,FThe 98-year-old added: "To speak to
OL,12,Fother comrades, it's incredible, and
OL,13,Fpeople that have done a lot more than
OL,14,Fme. I'm one of the young ones."
OL,16,FIt's an event that's brought the
