OL,6,FSwansea Council Leader Rob Stewart
OL,7,Fsaid: "Without the efforts of the
OL,8,Fpeople here today, we wouldn't have
OL,9,Fthe freedoms that we enjoy. So it's
OL,10,Freally nice for us to say thank you to
OL,11,Fthem and to give them a lovely
OL,12,Fafternoon.
OL,14,F"It's really important that we do this
OL,15,Fand take time to honour our veterans
OL,16,Fand I couldn't be prouder to be doing
OL,17,Fit."
